c: 4
v: 155
t: "Nokuti vakatyora chitsidzo, uye vakaramba humboo hwaAllah, uye kuuraya kwavaiita vatumwa vasina mvumo, uye nemashoko avo (ekuti): “Moyo yedu yakaputirwa (hatinzwisisi mashoko evatumwa).” Kwete, Allah vakaisa chivharo pamoyo yavo nekuda kwekusatenda kwavo, saka havatendi kusara kwekadimbu"